<h1>Application Not Approved</h1>

<p>Hello <%= @user.display_name %>,</p>

<p>Thank you for your interest in joining <%= @organization %>. After careful review, we are not able to approve your membership application at this time.</p>

<% if @reason.present? %>
<p><strong>Additional information:</strong> <%= @reason %></p>
<% end %>

<p>If you have questions or believe this decision was made in error, please contact us.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>
The <%= @organization %> Team</p>
